---
title: Garlicky Sumac Chicken & Chickpea Bowls with Basmati Rice, Lemony Hummus Sauce & Parsley
description: This hearty spiced chicken and rice bowl will fill you up and warm you through and through. Lemony sumac-spiced chicken is seared to a golden brown while chickpeas roast alongside red onion wedges in a garlicky olive oil until crispy. It’s all served over a bed of fragrant basmati rice. And since the secret’s always in the sauce, you’ll finish things off with a drizzle of herby lemon hummus and a vibrant sprinkle of fresh parsley.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlicky-sumac-chicken-chickpea-bowls-64bc8283.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/garlicky-sumac-chicken-chickpea-bowls-63f4d8731c26d1ad5e0183b3-32a8ed19.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 820 kcal
  fat: 25 g
  saturated fat: 3 g
  carbohydrates: 96 g
  sugar: 9 g
  protein: 48 g
  fiber: 9 g
  sodium: 1060 mg
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/garlicky-sumac-chicken-and-chickpea-bowls-63f4d8731c26d1ad5e0183b3
